OL,3,CIran strike risks: Have we forgotten
OL,4,Cthe cautionary tale of Iraq?
OL,6,FBut at least we knew that regime
OL,7,Fchange, via the removal of this cruel
OL,8,Fdictator, was the goal.
OL,10,FWhat exactly will be the goal of US
OL,11,Fair strikes on Iran, if they happen?
OL,13,FThat question should be at the
OL,14,Fforefront of everyone's minds. But it
OL,15,Fjust isn't.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
