OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771952662
OL,3,CIran strike risks: Have we forgotten
OL,4,Cthe cautionary tale of Iraq?
OL,6,FHas the unpredictability of US
OL,7,FPresident Trump made us all so punch
OL,8,Fdrunk that the cautionary tale of Iraq
OL,9,Fhas been forgotten?
OL,11,FMr Trump won't spell out his
OL,12,Fobjectives, so he can never be accused
OL,13,Fof not meeting them.
OL,15,FIf this is his "help on the way", then
OL,16,Fthe strikes will be intended to
OL,17,Frekindle a protest movement that seems
OL,18,Fcrushed and dormant.
OL,26,@wD@POUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
