OL,3,CIran strike risks: Have we forgotten
OL,4,Cthe cautionary tale of Iraq?
OL,6,FIf this is to pressure Iran into
OL,7,Fconcessions on its nuclear programme,
OL,8,Fthen why Mr Trump, when you said last
OL,9,FJune that your bunker-busters had
OL,10,F"obliterated" the nuclear effort?
OL,12,FAt the end of what was a 12-day war,
OL,13,Fthe Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,14,FNetanyahu said "we've achieved a
OL,15,Fhistoric victory and this victory will
OL,16,Flast for generations".
OL,18,FNow it seems that victory lasted just
OL,19,Feight months.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@MO]vD@POUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
