OL,3,CIran strike risks: Have we forgotten
OL,4,Cthe cautionary tale of Iraq?
OL,6,FIt's undoubtedly true that the odious
OL,7,FIranian regime has never been weaker
OL,8,Fthan it is today. That makes this a
OL,9,Funique opportunity to weaken it
OL,10,Ffurther. But at what cost?
OL,12,FLast June, in retaliation for the US
OL,13,Fattack, the Iranians gave prior notice
OL,14,Fthey were going to target the al-Udeid
OL,15,Fair base in Qatar. They fired 14
OL,16,Fmissiles and despite the prior warning
OL,17,Fone of them got through the American
OL,18,Fdefensive shield.
OL,20,FWhat might a swarm of missiles do out
OL,21,Fof the blue?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
