CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771952662
OL,3,CIran strike risks: Have we forgotten
OL,4,Cthe cautionary tale of Iraq?
OL,6,FIn Israel, the Americans and the IDF
OL,7,Fmanaged to shoot down 85% of the
OL,8,FIranian ballistic missiles that they
OL,9,Ftried to intercept. But the 49 half-
OL,10,Fton warheads that got through damaged
OL,11,Fmore than 2,300 homes and killed 32
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FIran is thought to possess around
OL,15,F2,000 such missiles today.
OL,17,FAnd Iran has plenty of potential
OL,18,Ftargets far closer by than Israel:
OL,19,FAmerican bases in the Gulf.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
