OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1771952662
OL,3,CIran strike risks: Have we forgotten
OL,4,Cthe cautionary tale of Iraq?
OL,6,FMight their air defence systems be
OL,7,Foverwhelmed?
OL,9,FAnd if the Iranian regime does teeter
OL,10,Fand fall who might step in?
OL,12,FIran is also a patchwork of
OL,13,Fethnicities. Might not a bloody civil
OL,14,Fwar be a likely outcome? With
OL,15,Fspillover affecting near neighbours
OL,16,Flike Iraq, Afghanistan and Pakistan?
OL,18,FThere are many questions - or what the
OL,19,FUS Defence Secretary in 2003, Donald
OL,20,FRumsfeld, might have called "known
OL,21,Funknowns."
OL,26,@|D@]OU}D@JO]
